SIMPLE: goose_egg
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Goose egg
<hw>Goose egg</hw>. <sn>1.</sn> <def>In games, a zero; a score or record
of naught; -- so named in allusion to the egglike outline of the zero
sign 0. Called also <altname>duck egg</altname>.</def>
<mark>[Slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A bump on the skin caused by a blow, especially one
on the head.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Goosefish</ent>⟦br⟧
